data.description: Be Sure to Watch Video Walk Through. NO HOA/Metro. West Greeley Gem! This turn key home features almost 3,000 square feet finished, with new paint, carpet, light fixtures and real wood floors. This home has the extra touches that make it stand out. Covered RV parking with a 3 car wide driveway. Sun-drenched 20X10 Dining room for family gatherings. Large Custom brick window wells that create a Daylight basement.  Enjoy barbecues on your large patio overlooking your spacious privacy fenced yard. This home is perfectly situated on a quiet street and a desirable neighborhood. Don't miss this opportunity.
